---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="bg-ink text-white/70 mt-auto">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-12">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-10">
      <div class="md:col-span-2">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-4">
          <img src="/favicon.svg" alt="" class="w-7 h-7 brightness-0 invert opacity-80" width="28" height="28" />
          <span class="font-display text-lg text-white">Truffe.info</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed max-w-md">
          Progetto open source dedicato alla raccolta e diffusione di informazioni
          sulle truffe in Italia. Ogni segnalazione, anche di un tentativo non riuscito,
          contribuisce a proteggere gli altri.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 class="text-white text-sm font-semibold mb-4">Navigazione</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
          <li><a href="/truffe" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Tipi di truffa</a></li>
          <li><a href="/segnala" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Segnala una truffa</a></li>
          <li><a href="/database" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Database truffatori</a></li>
          <li><a href="/chi-siamo" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Chi siamo</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3 class="text-white text-sm font-semibold mb-4">Risorse utili</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
          <li><a href="/linee-guida" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Linee guida</a></li>
          <li><a href="/segnala-contenuto" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Segnala un contenuto</a></li>
          <li><a href="/privacy" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Privacy</a></li>
          <li><a href="/termini" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Termini</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="border-t border-white/10 mt-10 pt-6 flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-4 text-xs">
      <p>&copy; {year} Truffe.info — Progetto open source sotto licenza MIT</p>
      <div class="flex gap-4">
        <a href="/linee-guida" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Linee guida</a>
        <a href="/segnala-contenuto" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Segnala contenuto</a>
        <a href="/privacy" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Privacy</a>
        <a href="/termini" class="hover:text-white transition-colors">Termini</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
